Tz4RsUlX1pWCkLLPewu1vAAoTEzxzR\"\n                },\n                \"sequence\": \"1\",\n                \"signature\": \"6O2TQAgleFNPw4zIWBLaNvOf5dR7DHNSr2DwAPeFK6lokRqZd2KR2BD+WlmaWj4LdLo5N+utN1JtY41E91N0uw==\"\n            }\n        ],\n        \"source\": \"0\"  // fixed, source of the transaction\n    }\n}\n```\n"
